        "Data": [
          "<h1>Applies to</h1>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>PCI DSS Requirement 10.2.4</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <h1>What to Do</h1>\r\n  <p>Log failed access attempts.</p>\r\n  <h1>Why</h1>\r\n  <p>Failed access attempts may be an indication of an attack.</p>\r\n  <h1>How</h1>\r\n  <p>This functionality should be implemented by the centralized log server solution. Follow the vendor's instructions to configure the log server to log failed access attempts.\r\n</p>"
